snippet.title: Cave Digger 2: Dig Harder Full Release Trailer | Cave Digger VR Game Series by VRKiwi
snippet.description:
Cave Digger 2 full Release is finally here, yay!
Go on an enigmatic adventure in this 1-4 player VR game set in an alternative western world. Discoveries, dangers and digging await the Prospector.

Get Cave Digger 2 from: 
Steam 👉 https://bit.ly/3GUffnc
App Lab 👉 https://ocul.us/36zTs7u
SideQuest 👉 https://bit.ly/3IPRY66
PlayStation 👉 https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10002212
⛏️🤠 Join our Discord for 'saloon' talks and upcoming news https://discord.gg/cavedigger 
🐦You can also get the latest news by following us on Twitter https://twitter.com/vr_kiwi
Cave Digger on Facebook https://www.facebook.com/cavediggergame
Developer streams on Twitch https://www.twitch.tv/vrkiwigaming
Developer blog – get to know us behind the scenes https://vrkiwi.org/what-vr/cave-digger-2-dev-blog/
We are on TikTok too https://www.tiktok.com/@vrkiwi
VRKiwi on Facebook https://www.facebook.com/VRKiwiEntertainment/
and on LinkedIn https://www.linkedin.com/company/vrkiwi

Good gaming.
